text: The High Commissioner of Malaysia to Canada is the head of Malaysia's diplomatic mission to Canada. The position has the rank and status of an Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary and is based in the High Commission of Malaysia, Ottawa. ==List of heads of mission== ===Chargé d'Affaires to Canada=== {| class=wikitable !
